====Usage notes====
留 takes the vowel-initial [[allomorph]] {{m|oko|乙留}} or {{m|oko|乙以}} after a consonant, corresponding exactly to the Middle and Modern Korean allomorph {{okm-inline|으로|ulo}} also appearing after a consonant.

====Reconstruction notes====
Conventionally reconstructed as {{IPAfont|*-lwo}} after the Middle Korean reflex, although the source Chinese readings suggest a different vowel. Many scholars suggest {{IPAfont|*-lwu}} instead.

